<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>链接已失效</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: "PingFang SC","Microsoft YaHei",sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: #F5F7FA;
    }
    .box {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 48px 32px;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
      max-width: 360px;
      width: 90%;
    }
    .icon { font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    h2 { color: #FF4D4F; font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    p { color: #999; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="box">
    <div class="icon">&#9203;</div>
    <h2>链接已失效</h2>
    <p>该分享链接已过期或已被停用，请联系管理员获取新的分享链接。</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
